<br>
Better shields would have to be much better, it is hard to imagine a combination of additional AC, HP, and resists that would be worth giving up the off-hand for dual wielding classes.<br>
<br>
Most of the caster <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>&quot;shields&quot;</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> I recall seeing have resists, mostly MR, so that is consistant with <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>&quot;shields reflecting a bolt&quot;</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> and such.<br>
<br>
I think making bash worthwhile might be the key.<br>
